library(sf)
library(tidyverse)
library(elevatr)
library(rgdal)
library(readr)
library(raster)
library(osmdata)
library(leaflet)
library(climateR)
params = c("prcp", "tmax", "tmin", "swe")
AOI = USAboundaries::us_states() %>% filter(name == "California")
co = climateR::getTerraClim(AOI, params, startDate = "2018-01-01")  %>% 
  stack() %>% 
  setNames(params)
plot(co)

values = values(co)
head(values)
